  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Behold the sights of New England, all done in a Hidden Object style. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play over 30 fun minigames, all connected to New England! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up fun facts about the region! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Comes with wallpapers and a full soundtrack. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maximize your vacation with Unlimited Mode!</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>Collector's Edition</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 more chapters </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 CE-exclusive Hidden Object scenes!</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unearth the wonders of New England in a game that combines history, adventure, and hidden object challenges. 'Finding America: New England' takes you on an unforgettable journey. Seek out hidden objects amidst stunning scenery and unlock the stories of America's colonial past. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589350/extras/f83bd71736c9826ab6c3f09073a94b00.poster.avif?t=1729159387\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589350/extras/f83bd71736c9826ab6c3f09073a94b00.webm?t=1729159387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589350/extras/f83bd71736c9826ab6c3f09073a94b00.mp4?t=1729159387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589350/extras/f68fdc8752d6e0672a6ee276523973fb.poster.avif?t=1729159387\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589350/extras/f68fdc8752d6e0672a6ee276523973fb.webm?t=1729159387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589350/extras/f68fdc8752d6e0672a6ee276523973fb.mp4?t=1729159387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy one stunning chapter after another and experience all that New England has in store in this all-American Hidden Object game!</p>",
